               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED:</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Tetracaine Hydrochloride Ophthalmic Solution USP, 0.5% is supplied in a plastic bottle with a controlled drop tip in the following size:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>15 mL - Prod. No. 09111</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20160120"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="i4i_section_id_7e1e922d-8227-41e5-bcd5-20bcafe01c84">
               <id root="e7782810-a6b4-4cfa-a997-0cb6c40f87a7"/>
               <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
               <title>STORAGE:</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Store between 15°-25°C (59°-77°F). KEEP TIGHTLY CLOSED.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
